Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,DAI AND POPP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than burden Dai\Nand the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My life belongs to them,\Nbut if it will burden them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please! Don't go!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please stop walking gladly\Ninto death's arms!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You two will be executed\Nat noon in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Just kill us already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll choose death\Nover being used in some scheme!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But warriors of your caliber are valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially you, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept this Dark Aura and serve me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Say he's wasting his time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd sell your soul to Mystban\Njust to survive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were a man\Ntruly worthy of respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That you were my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd betray us\Nat the 11th hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you consider me a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to trust me no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A proud death is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I have this new feeling.\NUntil the final moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to cling to a chance at survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to rescue them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But this execution announcement\Nis clearly a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing that, we must be willing\Nto expend all of our forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything!\NThe world is going to end otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We must rally our forces\Nunder the Hero once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Once Dai's awake, let's have him\Ngive a speech to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's willing to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone will\Nbe happy to fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Dai is everyone's Hero of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're right.\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he'll give everyone courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}still want to make me keep fighting!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check up on Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Gomechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how many members\Nthe Beast King Commandos has now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We even have ten members now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! I can't find Dai anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does everyone\Nexpect me to do the impossible?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My power's not enough.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's nothing I can do!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Dai ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't blame him. He's still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost his father in front of him,\Nalong with his greatest weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If that was on his mind,\Nwhy didn't he talk to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he doesn't understand\Nwhat tortures him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't run out of fear of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He fears the weight of his title.\NOf not knowing if he can live up to it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as cruel as it is, he's not\Na true Hero if he can't overcome himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a true Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Dai would leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,First it's Dai, now we have\N"The Uncharacteristic, Part Two."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected to see you\Nall fragile and weepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know what life brings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The first guy to run from danger\Nis still standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,With Hyunckel, Big Guy,\Nand of course with Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he used Rura to go far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rura, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'm in Teran.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,God of Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! May the mighty Hero\Ndefeat the Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Mighty Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so sorry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't answer your prayers.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The servant of your god told me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dark King Ban is stronger than a god.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no one who can touch him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I guess you can cry a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A moonlight walk could do you good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:59.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}MEDOROA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been with you since the very\Nbeginning back on Dermline Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no place\Nyou can go that I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rura spells are limited\Nto places you've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, back when I was\Ngetting used to using Rura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ended up in a place\Nimportant to me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Dark Forest where we first met Maam.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So I figured the same thing would happen\Nif you flew off randomly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place where\Nyou first met your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When we all should be working together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I knew Hyunckel\Nand Crocodine are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran from the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here to yell at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"You call yourself a Hero?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Coward."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I criticize\Nsomeone else about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to running,\NI'm way more experienced than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You fought as hard as you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your father, and your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You did... the best you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My best isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with this power,\NI couldn't do anything to the Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I let my father die,\Nand I let everyone get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to think Heroes were so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just idolized them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But then I met Leona.\NThen I met Master Aban.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And everyone called me a Hero.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I tried to become\Nas strong as I could for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,all my power wasn't nearly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not against Dark King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, they still think\NI can do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They still believe I'm a real Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If they all continue to fight\Nbelieving in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll all end up like Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then. I won't try to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But, even if you won't come,\NI'm going to fight the Dark King again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared of strong guys\Nand always running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I am, picking a fight\Nwith the God of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My battles have brought me this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming this far with you, Maam, Hyunckel,\Nand the others is my one point of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If I quit here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,all my days of fighting, building up what\Ncourage I have, will have been pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, we've always fought\Nfor someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To avenge Master Aban.\NTo reclaim peace for our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that's not\Nour only reason to fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not only for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to keep fighting for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. This is our fight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is... our fight.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You make up your own mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:14:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I still believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're\Na real Hero or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe because you're Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about a Hero?!\NWho cares about a Dragon Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll always be Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why bother asking...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when I've already decided?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I couldn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, couldn't you find Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The stage is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to go cool my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to worry all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, Dark King Ban is powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Mother Dragon said\Nhe's stronger than a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say that if we fight him\Nwe're going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm weaker than Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no special weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't just sit back and let him\Ntrample the world by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's one thing\NI have stronger than anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it's this belief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you will accept me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,please lend me your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at noon, we move to rescue\NHyunckel and Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be heading into a trap,\Nso we must be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, we must obtain\Nthe Great Purification Spell, Minakator.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Minakator?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's greater than Aban's Mahokator spell.\NIt can seal the Magic Power of Darklings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You said Ban Palace\Nhas a protective field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It keeps us from\Nusing Rura spells to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If Minakator works, it will erase\NBan Palace's field,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,allowing entry with a Rura spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a spell\Nnot even Aban could attain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If Master Aban couldn't cast it, who...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The fifth Disciple of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Disciples of Aban receive\Nthe Insignia of Aban from Master Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only four of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same! It's an insignia of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Then the fifth Disciple...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,These are made by polishing\Na rare stone called Kiseiseki,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and concentrating it with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,These are heirlooms of Aban's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Only he knows how to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These have the power to magnify holy power\Nand repel dark power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They work as charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,These Insignias have protected you\Nthrough all your battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never knew.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never even considered it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master Aban... Master Aban was always...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was watching over us.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I always assumed we made it this far\Nthrough our own strength, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Without these Insignias of Aban,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,we may have lost some battles by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban has always been\Nlending his strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban gave me this as a charm.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Afterwards, he came up with the idea to\Ngive them to his students upon graduation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to be\Nthe fifth Disciple of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe Aban would have chosen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I believe that you\Ncan attain Minakator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it will require\Nyou to pass a severe test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you accept this, Princess Leona?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona! This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, I'm going to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been frustrated that\NI couldn't share your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I should fight like Popp and Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept it!\NNo matter what test awaits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, I will truly be\Na member of your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The test will be to brave\Nthe Cave of Trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a labyrinth teeming with monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Only there can you bind with\Nthe Minakator spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But can I become a Disciple of Aban\Nwithout his teachings?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I tell you a little bit about Aban?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:12.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:18.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:23.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:29.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:35.64,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:41.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:47.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:53.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:59.21,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:01.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:05.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:10.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:16.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:22.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:25.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:30.07,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the Dark Lord Hadorra\Ninvaded the world,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.91,0:23:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Order of Carl, led by Princess Flora,\Nfearlessly faced his Dark Army.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban guarded Carl Kingdom\Nwith his captain, Roka.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With a fateful encounter with Hadorra,\Nhis destiny was set in motion.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days of Aban's youth are revealed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.22,0:23:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Aban, the Hero"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.39,0:24:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
